ing a good life), most of all for the astronomical wild-invertebrate populations. Combined with the meat-eater problem it drives human charities firmly net-negative — every human sustained means more net-negative farmed lives. Presupposes counting wild/invertebrate animals, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; and like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans). || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 8 net_negative_animal_lives" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx9Vttu4zYQ%2FZWB0aJ24DiyNlcXfsjFuWC93SDrdlHEgUJLI4tdihRIKoqazb93KPka230y7Rkenpk5h%2FRbI8KY5cJeqggbvcbBAfT7fRhpxiVYBaFm%2F5a0KCSMc9%2FrHkKhtIheOBZQdAM%2FOAqOg1NoGqsyOG25zWNJIOfG5GlmuZIQJoTVAw8yplWYcCYcVPfMhy7ETAesYGWQ5CmTZh7wgUmeMmECo1IsEmbnkaNFJGXWIu0OhFpEj8HkcYyay2kQqzA3GM1DpyDRBhKnzPIXDGqUQNDaVIQHLEyALVlzAwzuS5vQOuYCgfqxDJsDsI4ViyLTBo3URC7RgNIVmMZ9KpalSAy5od9tgnUffjMQ5zKsMH6HUKWZMsR2mUB7ZYSESD%2FxmpqxTEZMKImQ0pREB54XQxi8PDuqbju%2BZhha2vjCRI6g4gphOa9OBXaBxsIkLyF3x7iNBlcL68G3RPM0g%2B8oaDoI91r9Q7j17pvBH4OH89HgCiYlTFGiZhY7WTkXB0bcrrVpj4JtkDSiiozrJCFVWFdcEy4gDYw%2BqM3oRqD0lHqUEQWmS5jQETEPOa3bcDG4%2FvowoB5oJiqEAvk0sdQ%2B6ohQTq4Jf64nJ9RUKk0jhjPvV7i8g6bSVO%2B%2BivdTNpXc5hHCxdfR4LJFfIzKs8%2FchgnKKybKe9R%2Fmgj68DaWABmqTOAtigyjRcTreEfuQK9z5HIKFGKCxOSGRugg6hSvW%2Bd4XZcUqlySIGIW2pyJCyZ%2F%2FFVNyqV%2B2nHS3hboPWh2YX8XXGss38dyGq0V4rh4hzMynj%2BWLI03Ej7NKvJ8ost4upEwr8anmm0i1uLdju%2BihyfUzSJbD%2Fme52Inh0RiLAsuokk%2BNes5x3XOqV%2FlMCFi3CzBX7ScDFIo9TGjijsEb6axwWNxdT78G9gLameNjCT%2Fy1NvVWrRmgwtT2d2XcosVBQkEaK0HyxF29mHiw6y3BqnZu4sY0LlrNyHRzffN6C%2BYw%2FGjaEKSZpOdvCj1t240YYiWpTTgxSZbG4VZosUQIqB9%2FY66A1dZrWpRLkdblUV%2F4dC3hfgbnQqSXNbQvP8y3VrO%2BaakhzoJuT53Rc4gMsZ1kBajRldc5hrk%2FBsB%2Byq%2FnZxHdGcbt3LgTBENs1xO9aaVh1Wt3NGT8JHtO0X347BrGq8puefnG1Afiet08thCMdAM6mpZnQFk5wiNDtauumQ%2BoTu0WZrh8PrwdWOFn4wUQWyZThgWIxuyA%2B1qeCB3gSmw2QHvQ3vLYGfnO8