 requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 10 two_envelope_welfare_skepticism" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx9Vm1z4jYQ%2Fis7TDuFDCGGS7gLHT6QhLxMuV4mR5vphIwj7DVWI0seScZxc%2Fnvt7IJLwH6KYRdPfvs7vNIvNZCjFgm7LkKsdarHR1Bv9%2BHsWZcglUQaPZfQR9yCZOs47WPIVdahHOOOeRtv%2BOf%2BF2%2F7UHdWJVC22u44xNJMANjsiS1XEkIYkLrgQcp0yqIORMOrH3agTZETPssZ4UfZwmT5j3QASZ5woTxjUowj5l9j5wsIwmzFum0L9Qy2gWTRRFqLmd%2BpILMYLis5YHNlY9yjkKl6OcoqDj65hmJZsBNUvIesiAGtiLPDTC4LWxMnyMuEGgwq7A5AuvIsTA0TdBI0%2BQSDShdgmk8pJ5ZgkSUG%2FrexliN4zcDUSaDEuN3CFSSKkOkVwl0VoZIiPQVNyWasUyGTCiJkNC6RAueltsYzp8cVXccX1IMLB2cM5EhqKhEWC2uVYKdobEwzQrIXBl30OB6Yz0YE9a12wrCCNksw%2Brg1fDP4d1gPLyAaQEzlKiZxVZavAsEQ243JnRAwSZIWlLJww2RkEqsC66JKiCtjP7QhNFNX%2BkZjSfVtGZdwJRKRLQf%2BtyEs%2BHlt7shta%2BZKBFy5LPY0uRoGEI5ycb8qVqaUDOpNEkFTr1f4fwG6kpTq4cqOkzYTHKbhQhn38bD8wbxMSpL%2F%2BA2iFFeMFHcov7LhNCH14kESFGlAq9RpBguI17LO3EFvdaJyyE9iSkSkyvanoOoUrx2leO1XVKgMklaiFhgMybOmHz%2Bu1ySS%2F20p9LBDugDqLfhcB9cYyLfJnIWbjTiuHjHCzJeZyJZEm0lfFp05HWILuPJVsJ7Nx3q2cZiI95udVz0%2BDNNM083Qx3Pc7HPx0RiInMuwmk2M5s53SrnS6fMYUJEuN1CZzly8kau1MeMMu4QvIXGhg%2F5xWD0D7A5aueKlNT%2By2NvXWrhhgwtTxZOXcksUBQkEaK0H9xEx9mHqw7SzBqnZm6dsALlXNyHB7ffV6C5Yw8mtZEKSJpOdvBc6W5Sa0IeLtvpQYJM1ncKs0EKIMXAW3MT9IrPsTKVKHbDravi%2F1DuSXPgLnVqSXNbQH3w9bKxG3NDSQ50G3Jw8xWO4HyBNZRWY0o3HGbaxDzdA7uuv31ct26p3VgbWq2wTk%2B7W2jfY7p1Uriv3ga41epfmuWexaxrvIJ0DuuebKHek9zp3TAEZaAeV2xTuoBJUSGaPVPdNokr0sVDb7vCYDS6HF7sGeMHI5VUdywIDIvQLfquMhbc0ZPAdBDv4bflvxXwo%2FOepuvIPWl9GHFjWxrJgAbr5T9GaXtW1CtvNOH1x8sPeGmt1Xhr0CU2dW9UHxZAD97jwtLjna%2Fc%2BPrm%2B8qXPSh%2FNXCa%2BPT9qSPHc2JhyJVrDydVcBnr1Sey9vYTgBMTFg%3D%3D" id="w1_2_5_6_10"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#d7c6e6;strokeColor=#6a3fa0;fontColor=#2c1650;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="981" y="956" width="172" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Count soil animals&lt;br&gt;(~10^1